beer.beer_description: Pure Pastry is a brand new Imperial Pastry Stout that we have whipped up for this years stout season release for those of you who like them extra syrupy. Using our house vanilla processing method to extract extra goodness, we've assaulted Pure Pastry with a huge quantity of cacao nibs and vanilla beans. The result? Just like a chocolate milkshake, only the adult version! Rich and creamy with an addition of lactose, with flavours of dreamy milk chocolate, coco pops, cookies and cream ice cream. All backed up by a big body and syrupy mouthfeel. It's like drinking dessert in a glass!
